1
00:00:07,440 --> 00:00:08,440
Who are you?

2
00:00:08,440 --> 00:00:09,680
Why do you want to kill me?

3
00:00:09,680 --> 00:00:12,680
Zhang Yuehua.

4
00:00:20,080 --> 00:00:23,560
Fei Yufei.

5
00:00:20,080 --> 00:00:23,560
Deng Yining.

6
00:00:26,840 --> 00:00:28,800
Li Wanying.

7
00:00:26,840 --> 00:00:28,800
Fu Xinyan.

8
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:30,280
Li Wanying, Xia Zhi.

9
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:30,280
Fu Xinyan, Pei.

10
00:00:40,560 --> 00:00:44,000
Ding Lei.

11
00:00:40,560 --> 00:00:44,000
Su Zhinan.

12
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:49,280
Ding Doudou.

13
00:00:50,920 --> 00:00:52,560
Ding Doudou.

14
00:00:50,920 --> 00:00:52,560
Liu Ju.

15
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:54,060
Leave no one alive.

16
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:55,800
Don't run!

17
00:01:01,600 --> 00:01:02,440
Who are you?

18
00:01:02,440 --> 00:01:04,519
Why do you want to destroy the Zhu family?

19
00:01:04,519 --> 00:01:05,880
Go ask the King of Hell.

20
00:01:11,160 --> 00:01:13,680
I told you to find the Zhu family's secret recipe.

21
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:15,440
The Zhu family has been wiped out.

22
00:01:15,440 --> 00:01:17,120
Yet you tell me you found nothing.

23
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:18,880
I sent men to search through the night.

24
00:01:18,880 --> 00:01:21,039
But we haven't found it yet.

25
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:22,960
Useless idiots.

26
00:01:22,960 --> 00:01:25,680
Zhang Yuehua.

27
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:26,360
If you can't find it at the Zhu residence, look elsewhere!

28
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:27,560
I don't want excuses.

29
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:29,120
I just want the secret recipe.

30
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:31,320
Liang Jingyu.

31
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:30,440
I don't care how you do it.

32
00:01:31,320 --> 00:01:31,560
Get out!

33
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:32,090
Yes, sir.

34
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:45,759
Miss Zhu.

35
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:48,280
I haven't found the culprit behind the massacre yet,

36
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:51,360
but I found the one who tried to harm you in the wedding room.

37
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:53,520
It's the movie star, Yao Lifu.

38
00:01:53,880 --> 00:01:55,880
His relationship with Song Huainan

39
00:01:56,160 --> 00:01:57,720
seems rather unusual.

40
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:04,560
Yao Lifu's sister,

41
00:02:04,880 --> 00:02:05,880
Yao Shengsheng,

42
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:07,800
has been caught.

43
00:02:20,079 --> 00:02:21,140
What are you doing?

44
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:25,560
Of course, I'll take your face,

45
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,840
use the Yao family,

46
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:33,560
and find out the truth.

47
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:40,560
About my face swap,

48
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,740
don't tell anyone.

49
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:42,690
Don't worry.

50
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:44,900
We won't leak our patients' privacy.

51
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:49,320
Song Huainan,

52
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:51,960
regarding the massacre of the Zhu family,

53
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:53,760
how much were you involved?

54
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:56,160
And what is your relationship

55
00:02:56,160 --> 00:02:57,560
with the Yao family?

56
00:03:00,920 --> 00:03:01,800
One bam.

57
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:08,840
Young Marshal Song has arrived.

58
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:29,800
The Second Young Master of the Song family, Song Qingzhou.

59
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:32,040
He usually looks happy-go-lucky,

60
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:35,400
but don't be fooled by appearances.

61
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:37,500
He is extremely vigilant.

62
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:38,880
Be careful.

63
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:43,490
Shengsheng.

64
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:46,280
Yao Lifu,

65
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:49,480
you accomplice to the murder of the Zhu family!

66
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:51,720
Brother.

67
00:03:55,760 --> 00:03:57,220
You look beautiful today.

68
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,960
Marshal Song has arrived.

69
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,279
Uncle Yao.

70
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:19,839
I was busy with work, so I arrived a bit late.

71
00:04:19,839 --> 00:04:21,800
Let me drink this toast first

72
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,220
to show my respect.

73
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:35,400
Luo Li.

74
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:36,920
I want to make you

75
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:38,960
the happiest woman in Jiangcheng.

76
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:47,280
Song Huainan.

77
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:49,240
I'm back.

78
00:04:57,960 --> 00:04:58,600
Miss Yao.

79
00:04:58,800 --> 00:04:59,760
Long time no see.

80
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:01,760
You've become even more beautiful.

81
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:06,120
He looks like the one who killed me.

82
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:11,640
Miss Yao.

83
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,320
May I have this dance?

84
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:46,600
I'm sorry.

85
00:05:46,840 --> 00:05:47,700
It's all right.

86
00:05:47,960 --> 00:05:48,560
Excuse me.

87
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:49,880
I have to go.

88
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,520
It really is him.

89
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:15,360
Song Huainan's adjutant.

90
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:18,160
The Yaos and the Songs.

91
00:06:18,840 --> 00:06:21,400
I will make you pay.

